Class BaseAction<M extends BaseModel>

java.lang.Object
br.com.concepting.framework.controller.action.BaseAction<M>
Type Parameters:

public abstract class BaseAction<M extends BaseModel> extends Object
Class that defines the basic implementation of the form actions.
